{"tid":105029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙特空軍獲最強F-15戰機 : F15-SA","createTime":"2017-02-02T14:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T01:56:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c31f3f71d70dbcdf38d3325988b6a77985060bf","tid":105029,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:39:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170202/photo/bknint-20170202154131963-0202_17011_001_01b.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170202%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170202154131963-0202_17011_001_01b.jpg&d=m7n5JD7ZMd19sx07z0x1QJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=9faf521c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170202/photo/bknint-20170202154131963-0202_17011_001_01b.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n沙特阿拉伯及以色列是中東兩大空軍強國，都向盟友美國購買戰機。沙特日前正式對外公開，最新引入的美製F-15SA多用途戰機。由於戰機採用先進技術，加上可搭載大量武器，被視為F-15戰機系列中最強的一款，令沙特軍力如虎添翼。<br />\n<br />\n首批F-15SA早於去年12月13日飛抵沙特，但軍方於上月25日才對外公開這款戰機。F-15SA採用大量先進技術，包括配備有源相控陣雷達、數碼化玻璃駕駛艙、數碼電子作戰系統、導彈警報系統等。它設有11個掛點，可以搭載多款空對空及空對地導彈。沙特軍方上月29日發放影片，展示F-15SA的飛行性能。<br />\n<br />\n沙特於2011年底與美國簽署軍火協議，購買84架F-15SA，同時為現役的68架F-15S升級至F-15SA，總值294億美元，令沙特日後將擁有152架F-15SA。分析指，F-15SA的性能接近第5代隱形戰機，將負責壓制及摧毀敵方防空系統、發動空中反擊，同時在遠距離投放武器。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170202/photo/bknint-20170202154131963-0202_17011_001_03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170202%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170202154131963-0202_17011_001_03b.jpg&h=18363562&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dc8990f9d40156196f21bcc4cbcc685fd56904b","tid":105029,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e54b706626a886e9129869298c1eb0fcec6bdc55","tid":105029,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"唔係se先最勁咩"},{"pid":"b568c8b57a1e5b1cb4b74905efc47bc2a9b0683f","tid":105029,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係se先最勁咩</blockquote><br />\niphone se"},{"pid":"265f35b946fb54658b553a83294a47d8fdce92c1","tid":105029,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係se先最勁咩</blockquote><br />\nSe好似最後無量產<br />\n其實沙地既F15 SA 韓國既F15 K 同埋新加坡既F15 SG 都係出自F15 E 名稱唔同既原因係廠商會因應客戶既要求而度身訂造戰鬥機"},{"pid":"f62f28eb31d5841d202071e3d05baadf5601c4b1","tid":105029,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"Genesis: God bless israel and saudi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15804ed2b3f1ae63ecfc8c41186a37e23fda707c","tid":105029,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}